short_desc: Comprehensive library materials, services and resources for adults and children, including computers with Internet access
description: Consists of popular and well-reviewed juvenile and adult non-fiction and fiction books, DVDs, videos, audio books, CDs, magazines, and newspapers.Branch is home to the largest Lesbian/Gay/Transgender collection of fiction and non-fiction in the East Bay, established in 1994. It contains about 1,000 popular and contemporary titles.The branch is equipped with three computers with internet access for public use.
